<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="author" content="Maximiliano Joaquin Carrillo y Sofia Trinidad Yañez">
    <meta name="description" content="Las mejores zapatillas deportivas deportivas están en Moffy Sports">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Moffy Sports, MoffySports, Moffy">
    <title>Moffy Sports</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://necolas.github.io/normalize.css/8.0.1/normalize.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/productDetail.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/750a5cf973.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="content-detalle">

          <div class="img-detalle">
            <img src="/images/products/<%= producto.image %>" alt="Adidas Forum Low Azules" title="Adidas Forum Low Azules">
            <div class="zapatillas-colores">
                <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/b5/fe/9b/b5fe9b5ce2a87871c254581b91d55ced.jpg" alt="Adidas Forum Low verdes" title="Adidas Forum Low verdes">
                <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/e5/5c/b6/e55cb636f03586a6c639b8685cc193cc.jpg" alt="Adidas Forum Low rojas" title="Adidas Forum Low rojas">
                <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/4b/95/6b/4b956b452b1feb7218e4361ba803e1ac.jpg" alt="Adidas Forum Low blancas" title="Adidas Forum Low blancas">
            </div>
          </div>

          <section class="detalle">
            <h1><%= producto.name %></h1>
            <p>Precio: <strong>$<%= producto.price %></strong></p>
            <p>Marca: <strong><%= producto.category %></strong></p>
            <p>Opciones</p>
            <div class="button">
              <% producto.talles.map(talle => { %>
                <button>Talle <%= talle %></button>
              <% }) %>
            </div>
            <p>Color</p>
            <div class="button">
              <% producto.colors.map(color => { %>
                <button><%= color[0].toUpperCase() + color.substring(1) %></button>
              <% }) %>
            </div>
            <% if (producto.stock > 0) { %>
              <p>Stock disponible</p>
            <% } else { %>
              <p>Producto sin stock</p>
            <% } %>
            <form action="/products/<%=producto.id %>?_method=DELETE" method="post">
              <button class="button-carrito" type="submit">Anadir al carrito</button>
            </form>
          </section>
        </section>
        <section class="container-descripcion">
          <article>
             <h3>Descripcion</h3>
             <p>
                <%= producto.description %>
             </p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <h3>Opiniones</h3>
             <p>Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Deleniti commodi neque voluptatibus earum minus beatae praesentium ullam rem iste ratione. Porro eveniet quo, sint at dolor rerum ut quod optio! Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Iste quae, atque dolore suscipit quidem odit explicabo, debitis earum neque totam autem ullam modi praesentium voluptate quo. Officiis tenetur reiciendis temporibus. Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aliquam explicabo quo nam placeat ipsam unde voluptate ea. Deserunt beatae nihil ullam qui est sint blanditiis commodi ut illo ratione. Rem.</p>
          </article>
          <div class="img-sugerencias">
            <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/5c/51/a2/5c51a209e615c9c596d7c77aa628aafc.jpg" alt="Adidas Forum Low" title="Adidas Forum Low">
            <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/77/80/18/778018415c5cddeb8b56b65e61efc70b.jpg" alt="Adidas Forum Low" title="Adidas Forum Low">
            <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/a1/32/f0/a132f060431555e577770e7bfe6cbe55.jpg" alt="Adidas Forum Low" title="Adidas Forum Low">
            <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/75/eb/6d/75eb6d38f1f42218cbf229c9218724ff.jpg" alt="Adidas Forum Low" title="Adidas Forum Low">
            <img src=https://i.pinimg.com/564x/84/d6/b2/84d6b276d0cebf8329362b6a3e3cac3e.jpg alt="Adidas Forum Low" title="Adidas Forum Low">
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="sugerencias">
        </section> 
      </main>
      <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>